Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.49,oped,,0,0,0,,你是否滿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:31.83,oped,,0,0,0,,睜開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.24,oped,,0,0,0,,就能看到光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:36.71,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,579)}跨越這條新界線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:47.55,oped,,0,0,0,,被擊倒在地 不住地嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:51.76,oped,,0,0,0,,不斷抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:56.52,oped,,0,0,0,,遙遠的光芒 穿透黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:01.06,oped,,0,0,0,,那是心懷信念之人的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:06.03,oped,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get low！Hey! 咆哮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:10.53,oped,,0,0,0,,現在就行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:15.62,oped,,0,0,0,,Hey！你定會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.46,oped,,0,0,0,,蒼穹之Exodus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.83,oped,,0,0,0,,將那殘存的夢想higher
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.34,oped,,0,0,0,,不想再失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:27.09,oped,,0,0,0,,決不聽信liar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:30.13,oped,,0,0,0,,期待著 yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:34.01,oped,,0,0,0,,直至死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.39,oped,,0,0,0,,壁壘越高 則越發desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.77,oped,,0,0,0,,向敞開的心扉中messiah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.31,oped,,0,0,0,,想要抓住變遷的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:44.77,oped,,0,0,0,,決不放棄 yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:49.40,oped,,0,0,0,,超越那被囚禁的黑夜
